UKFN Early career researchers are invited to attend a meeting aimed at bringing together ECRs across all UKFN SIGs.
The event is intended to be an informal meeting where ECRs can have the opportunity to present their work with a talk or a poster, interact with each other, listen to advices for fellowships or job applications. It concludes with a social gathering at the pub.
There is also the possibility of subsidised travel depending on the number of attendees.
Interested in attending this event? Please send a registration email specifying your contribution format (poster/talk) before the 11th of March to:
Andrew Edwards: lfego Ruiz-Gutirrez: Jack Panter:
